==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Lave
<hw>Lave</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To bathe; to wash one's
self.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In her chaste current oft the goddess <qex>laves</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lave</ent>⟦br⟧

